lead_paragraph: With rain halting play everywhere except Centre Court at Wimbledon on Wednesday, number three seed Agnieska Radwanska was ready to become an armchair fan after her 6-2 6-1 first-round win over Ukraine's Kateryna Kozlova.

headline.print_headline: Radwanska Settles In for Afternoon of TV Tennis
